      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/chinese-exports-drop-in-blow-to-hopes-for-economic-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月份中国出口大幅下滑，对海外销售的蓬勃发展将抵消国内需求疲软并推动世界第二大经济体增长的希望造成打击。]]></description>
